data.description: Dream property! Beautiful 3 story home & approximately 15 acres with a huge 3 bay shop ideally located on scenic Hwy 14E just minutes from the Ozark National Forest, Blanchard Springs Caverns, the Buffalo National & White Rivers, & the music & festivals in world renown Mountain View! Enjoy beautiful sunrises, sunsets, & mountain views from the privacy of your covered front porch swing. This well maintained home comes furnished & offers 3 bedrooms with 2 other large bonus areas for use as 2 additional bedrooms, an office, game room, or den. The shop includes a lift, tools, surround sound, bar or office area, & wood stove. There is also a small storage shed with a lean-to perfect to store your lawnmower & ATV's. The acreage has marketable timber, an abundance of whitetail deer & small game, a stock pond, & trails for ATV riding. Public water, private septic, electric co-op, fiber internet availability. Kitchen appliances & washer/dryer convey. Move-in ready! One of a kind find! Call today to set up a viewing.
